snippet.title: AMBER HEARD Coming To The MCU As Sue Storm In FANTASTIC FOUR | Amber Heard Jumps From DCEU TO MCU |
snippet.description:
Please watch: "Spiderman No Way Home Post Credit Scenes Revealed" 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VYnBFydRXtI --~--
Amber Heard moves from DCEU TO MCU to join Fantastic Four. What you think about this casting?

Let us know in the comments section down below.

This video includes:
Ben Affleck, Ryan Reynolds, Josh Brolin, Chas Evans, Henry Cavill, Idris Elba, Gal Gadot, Tom Hardy, Michael Fassbender, Hugo Weaving, James Marsden, Natalie Portman, Christian Bale, Laurence Fishburne, Zoe Saldana, Heath Ledger, Jared Leto
